short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension will help you to end boring google meet sessions even if you are in deep sleep

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Sometimes you are forced to attend some Google meetings even though it is irrelevant to you. In such cases you have to be stayed in meeting room throughout and have to close meeting when it ends, otherwise you will be the only person remaining and other team members will have an impression that you were not listening to the discussion. 

To avoid such situations you can use this plugin to end meet sessions automatically even if you are not near the system. Please ensure the tab is active when you are away ;).
